{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":290,"text":"I'm a physician trained in infectious diseases,"},{"time":5538,"text":"and following my training,"},{"time":7932,"text":"I moved to Somalia"},{"time":10854,"text":"from San Francisco."},{"time":12898,"text":"And my goodbye greeting"},{"time":14513,"text":"from the chief of infectious diseases"},{"time":16366,"text":"at San Francisco General was,"},{"time":18462,"text":"\"Gary, this is the biggest mistake you'll ever make.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":22145,"text":"But I landed in a refugee situation"},{"time":26193,"text":"that had a million refugees in 40 camps,"},{"time":30266,"text":"and there were six of us doctors."},{"time":32793,"text":"There were many epidemics there."},{"time":35109,"text":"My responsibilities were largely related to"},{"time":37722,"text":"tuberculosis,"},{"time":39463,"text":"and then we got struck by an epidemic of cholera."},{"time":43329,"text":"So it was the spread of tuberculosis"},{"time":45392,"text":"and the spread of cholera"},{"time":47439,"text":"that I was responsible for inhibiting."},{"time":52640,"text":"And in order to do this work, we, of course,"},{"time":55281,"text":"because of the limitation in health workers,"},{"time":57981,"text":"had to recruit refugees to be a specialized"},{"time":61747,"text":"new category of health worker."},{"time":64506,"text":"Following three years of work in Somalia,"},{"time":67734,"text":"I got picked up by the World Health Organization,"},{"time":70344,"text":"and got assigned to the epidemics of AIDS."},{"time":73391,"text":"My primary responsibility was Uganda,"},{"time":76264,"text":"but also I worked in Rwanda and Burundi"},{"time":79267,"text":"and Zaire, now Congo,"},{"time":82354,"text":"Tanzania, Malawi, and several other countries."},{"time":85922,"text":"And my last assignment there was to run a unit"},{"time":88383,"text":"called intervention development,"},{"time":90268,"text":"which was responsible for designing interventions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":93984,"text":"After 10 years of working overseas,"},{"time":96959,"text":"I was exhausted."},{"time":98682,"text":"I really had very little left."},{"time":100880,"text":"I had been traveling to one country after another."},{"time":105292,"text":"I was emotionally feeling very isolated."},{"time":108756,"text":"I wanted to come home."},{"time":110894,"text":"I'd seen a lot of death,"},{"time":112930,"text":"in particular epidemic death,"},{"time":115880,"text":"and epidemic death has a different feel to it."},{"time":118828,"text":"It's full of panic and fear,"},{"time":122436,"text":"and I'd heard the women wailing and crying"},{"time":126247,"text":"in the desert."},{"time":128540,"text":"And I wanted to come home and take a break"},{"time":130933,"text":"and maybe start over."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133972,"text":"I was not aware of any epidemic problems"},{"time":136824,"text":"in America."},{"time":138461,"text":"In fact, I wasn't aware of any problems in America."},{"time":141748,"text":"In fact -- seriously."},{"time":143828,"text":"And in fact I would visit friends of mine,"},{"time":146670,"text":"and I noticed that they had water"},{"time":149759,"text":"that came right into their homes."},{"time":151772,"text":"How many of you have such a situation?"},{"time":153647,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":154815,"text":"And some of them, many of them actually,"},{"time":157426,"text":"had water that came into more than one room."},{"time":159541,"text":"And I noticed that they would move"},{"time":162788,"text":"this little thermoregulatory device"},{"time":164795,"text":"to change the temperature in their home"},{"time":167070,"text":"by one degree or two degrees."},{"time":169921,"text":"And now I do that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":171602,"text":"And I really didn't know what I would do,"},{"time":175855,"text":"but friends of mine began telling me"},{"time":178400,"text":"about children shooting other children with guns."},{"time":182380,"text":"And I asked the question,"},{"time":184195,"text":"what are you doing about it?"},{"time":186153,"text":"What are you in America doing about it?"},{"time":188261,"text":"And there were two essential explanations"},{"time":190673,"text":"or ideas that were prevalent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":192922,"text":"And one was punishment."},{"time":194976,"text":"And this I had heard about before."},{"time":197149,"text":"We who had worked in behavior"},{"time":199793,"text":"knew that punishment was something that was discussed"},{"time":203177,"text":"but also that it was highly overvalued."},{"time":206014,"text":"It was not a main driver of behavior,"},{"time":208358,"text":"nor was it a main driver of behavior change."},{"time":212248,"text":"And besides that, it reminded me"},{"time":214298,"text":"of ancient epidemics"},{"time":216800,"text":"that were previously completely misunderstood"},{"time":219870,"text":"because the science hadn't been there before,"},{"time":222444,"text":"epidemics of plague"},{"time":224830,"text":"or typhus or leprosy,"},{"time":227742,"text":"where the prevalent ideas were that there were"},{"time":230479,"text":"bad people or bad humors or bad air,"},{"time":234121,"text":"and widows were dragged around the moat,"},{"time":236730,"text":"and dungeons were part of the solution."}]},{"cues":[{"time":240177,"text":"The other explanation or, in a way,"},{"time":242330,"text":"the solution suggested,"},{"time":244104,"text":"is please fix all of these things:"},{"time":247104,"text":"the schools, the community, the homes, the families,"},{"time":250436,"text":"everything."},{"time":251962,"text":"And I'd heard this before as well."},{"time":253775,"text":"I'd called this the \"everything\" theory,"},{"time":256510,"text":"or EOE: Everything On Earth."},{"time":259178,"text":"But we'd also realized"},{"time":260789,"text":"in treating other processes and problems"},{"time":264426,"text":"that sometimes you don't need to treat everything."}]},{"cues":[{"time":267341,"text":"And so the sense that I had"},{"time":269525,"text":"was there was a giant gap here."},{"time":272123,"text":"The problem of violence was stuck,"},{"time":274869,"text":"and this has historically been the case"},{"time":277135,"text":"in many other issues."},{"time":278297,"text":"Diarrheal diseases had been stuck."},{"time":279875,"text":"Malaria had been stuck."},{"time":281354,"text":"Frequently, a strategy has to be rethought."},{"time":283824,"text":"It's not as if I had any idea what it would look like,"},{"time":287114,"text":"but there was a sense that we would have to do"},{"time":290420,"text":"something with new categories of workers"},{"time":292673,"text":"and something having to do with behavior change"},{"time":294941,"text":"and something having to do with public education."}]},{"cues":[{"time":299050,"text":"But I began to ask questions"},{"time":301117,"text":"and search out the usual things"},{"time":303655,"text":"that I had been exploring before,"},{"time":305607,"text":"like, what do the maps look like?"},{"time":307140,"text":"What do the graphs look like?"},{"time":308590,"text":"What does the data look like?"},{"time":310629,"text":"And the maps of violence"},{"time":313025,"text":"in most U.S. cities"},{"time":314987,"text":"looked like this."},{"time":316979,"text":"There was clustering."},{"time":318643,"text":"This reminded me of clustering that we'd seen also"},{"time":321981,"text":"in infectious epidemics,"},{"time":323724,"text":"for example cholera."},{"time":325716,"text":"And then we looked at the maps,"},{"time":328083,"text":"and the maps showed this typical wave"},{"time":330797,"text":"upon wave upon wave,"},{"time":332590,"text":"because all epidemics"},{"time":333945,"text":"are combinations of many epidemics."},{"time":336519,"text":"And it also looked like infectious epidemics."},{"time":339623,"text":"And then we asked the question,"},{"time":341236,"text":"well what really predicts a case of violence?"},{"time":344778,"text":"And it turns out that the greatest predictor"},{"time":347023,"text":"of a case of violence is a preceding case of violence."},{"time":350331,"text":"Which also sounds like, if there is a case of flu,"},{"time":353561,"text":"someone gave someone a case of flu, or a cold,"},{"time":356461,"text":"or the greatest risk factor of tuberculosis"},{"time":358901,"text":"is having been exposed to tuberculosis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":361953,"text":"And so we see that violence is, in a way,"},{"time":364685,"text":"behaving like a contagious disease."},{"time":367844,"text":"We're aware of this anyway"},{"time":369394,"text":"even in our common experiences"},{"time":371330,"text":"or our newspaper stories"},{"time":373140,"text":"of the spread of violence from fights"},{"time":376264,"text":"or in gang wars or in civil wars"},{"time":379715,"text":"or even in genocides."}]},{"cues":[{"time":381973,"text":"And so there's good news about this, though,"},{"time":384545,"text":"because there's a way to reverse epidemics,"},{"time":387350,"text":"and there's really only three things that are done"},{"time":389356,"text":"to reverse epidemics,"},{"time":391224,"text":"and the first of it is interrupting transmission."},{"time":393864,"text":"In order to interrupt transmission,"},{"time":395790,"text":"you need to detect and find first cases."},{"time":399340,"text":"In other words, for T.B. you have to find somebody"},{"time":402354,"text":"who has active T.B. who is infecting other people."},{"time":405602,"text":"Make sense?"},{"time":407019,"text":"And there's special workers for doing that."},{"time":409283,"text":"For this particular problem,"},{"time":411142,"text":"we designed a new category of worker"},{"time":413457,"text":"who, like a SARS worker"},{"time":414802,"text":"or someone looking for bird flu,"},{"time":416663,"text":"might find first cases."},{"time":418410,"text":"In this case, it's someone who's very angry"},{"time":420611,"text":"because someone looked at his girlfriend"},{"time":422364,"text":"or owes him money,"},{"time":424150,"text":"and you can find workers and train them"},{"time":426619,"text":"into these specialized categories."}]},{"cues":[{"time":429733,"text":"And the second thing to do, of course,"},{"time":431383,"text":"is to prevent further spread,"},{"time":432884,"text":"that means to find who else has been exposed,"},{"time":436406,"text":"but may not be spreading so much right now"},{"time":438851,"text":"like someone with a smaller case of T.B.,"},{"time":441377,"text":"or someone who is just hanging out in the neighborhoods,"},{"time":444231,"text":"but in the same group,"},{"time":445857,"text":"and then they need to be, in a way,"},{"time":448154,"text":"managed as well,"},{"time":449527,"text":"particular to the specific disease process."}]},{"cues":[{"time":452878,"text":"And then the third part, the shifting the norms,"},{"time":455931,"text":"and that means a whole bunch of community activities,"},{"time":459231,"text":"remodeling, public education,"},{"time":461572,"text":"and then you've got what you might call"},{"time":463709,"text":"group immunity."},{"time":464931,"text":"And that combination of factors"},{"time":466819,"text":"is how the AIDS epidemic in Uganda"},{"time":469181,"text":"was very successfully reversed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":471618,"text":"And so what we decided to do in the year 2000"},{"time":474448,"text":"is kind of put this together in a way"},{"time":476368,"text":"by hiring in new categories of workers,"},{"time":478895,"text":"the first being violence interruptors."},{"time":481470,"text":"And then we would put all of this into place"},{"time":484132,"text":"in one neighborhood"},{"time":485567,"text":"in what was the worst police district"},{"time":487977,"text":"in the United States at the time."},{"time":489884,"text":"So violence interruptors hired from the same group,"},{"time":492627,"text":"credibility, trust, access,"},{"time":495612,"text":"just like the health workers in Somalia,"},{"time":498230,"text":"but designed for a different category,"},{"time":500497,"text":"and trained in persuasion,"},{"time":502469,"text":"cooling people down, buying time, reframing."},{"time":506247,"text":"And then another category of worker,"},{"time":508213,"text":"the outreach workers, to keep people"},{"time":510753,"text":"in a way on therapy for six to 24 months."},{"time":514123,"text":"Just like T.B., but the object is behavior change."},{"time":517782,"text":"And then a bunch of community activities"},{"time":519590,"text":"for changing norms."}]},{"cues":[{"time":521285,"text":"Now our first experiment of this"},{"time":523652,"text":"resulted in a 67-percent drop"},{"time":526329,"text":"in shootings and killings"},{"time":527800,"text":"in the West Garfield neighborhood of Chicago."}]},{"cues":[{"time":530197,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":532347,"text":"And this was a beautiful thing"},{"time":533707,"text":"for the neighborhood itself,"},{"time":535323,"text":"first 50 or 60 days, then 90 days,"},{"time":538215,"text":"and then there was unfortunately another shooting"},{"time":539994,"text":"in another 90 days,"},{"time":541513,"text":"and the moms were hanging out in the afternoon."},{"time":543953,"text":"They were using parks they weren't using before."},{"time":546351,"text":"The sun was out. Everybody was happy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":548488,"text":"But of course, the funders said, \"Wait a second,"},{"time":551678,"text":"do it again.\""},{"time":553005,"text":"And so we had to then, fortunately,"},{"time":556322,"text":"get the funds to repeat this experience,"},{"time":559081,"text":"and this is one of the next four neighborhoods"},{"time":561092,"text":"that had a 45-percent drop in shootings and killings."},{"time":564112,"text":"And since that time, this has been replicated"},{"time":566888,"text":"20 times."},{"time":568504,"text":"There have been independent evaluations"},{"time":570585,"text":"supported by the Justice Department"},{"time":572531,"text":"and by the CDC and performed by Johns Hopkins"},{"time":575308,"text":"that have shown 30-to-50-percent and 40-to-70-percent"},{"time":579102,"text":"reductions in shootings and killings"},{"time":581211,"text":"using this new method."},{"time":583133,"text":"In fact, there have been three independent"},{"time":584580,"text":"evaluations of this now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":586698,"text":"Now we've gotten a lot of attention as a result of this,"},{"time":588955,"text":"including being featured on"},{"time":591151,"text":"The New York Times' Sunday magazine cover story."},{"time":595096,"text":"The Economist in 2009"},{"time":597894,"text":"said this is \"the approach that will come to prominence.\""},{"time":600108,"text":"And even a movie was made around our work."},{"time":602445,"text":"[The Interrupters]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":603613,"text":"However, not so fast,"},{"time":606117,"text":"because a lot of people did not agree"},{"time":607979,"text":"with this way of going about it."},{"time":609960,"text":"We got a lot of criticism,"},{"time":611923,"text":"a lot of opposition,"},{"time":613662,"text":"and a lot of opponents."},{"time":615397,"text":"In other words, what do you mean, health problem?"},{"time":618248,"text":"What do you mean, epidemic?"},{"time":620834,"text":"What do you mean, no bad guys?"},{"time":623642,"text":"And there's whole industries designed"},{"time":625795,"text":"for managing bad people."},{"time":628753,"text":"What do you mean, hiring people"},{"time":631796,"text":"who have backgrounds?"},{"time":633745,"text":"My business friends said,"},{"time":638244,"text":"\"Gary, you're being criticized tremendously."},{"time":641591,"text":"You must be doing something right.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":643589,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":645598,"text":"My musician friends added the word \"dude.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":648853,"text":"So anyway, additionally,"},{"time":652624,"text":"there was still this problem,"},{"time":654449,"text":"and we were getting highly criticized as well"},{"time":657354,"text":"for not dealing with all of these other problems."},{"time":660650,"text":"Yet we were able to manage malaria"},{"time":663780,"text":"and reduce HIV and reduce diarrheal diseases"},{"time":666532,"text":"in places with awful economies"},{"time":668470,"text":"without healing the economy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":670290,"text":"So what's actually happened is,"},{"time":672825,"text":"although there is still some opposition,"},{"time":675270,"text":"the movement is clearly growing."},{"time":677090,"text":"Many of the major cities in the U.S.,"},{"time":679174,"text":"including New York City and Baltimore"},{"time":681412,"text":"and Kansas City,"},{"time":682677,"text":"their health departments are running this now."},{"time":684610,"text":"Chicago and New Orleans, the health departments"},{"time":687231,"text":"are having a very large role in this."},{"time":689762,"text":"This is being embraced more by law enforcement"},{"time":692617,"text":"than it had been years ago."},{"time":694596,"text":"Trauma centers and hospitals"},{"time":696650,"text":"are doing their part in stepping up."},{"time":698944,"text":"And the U.S. Conference of Mayors"},{"time":700837,"text":"has endorsed not only the approach"},{"time":703430,"text":"but the specific model."},{"time":705723,"text":"Where there's really been uptake even faster"},{"time":708972,"text":"is in the international environment,"},{"time":710969,"text":"where there's a 55-percent drop"},{"time":712725,"text":"in the first neighborhood in Puerto Rico,"},{"time":715149,"text":"where interruptions are just beginning in Honduras,"},{"time":717955,"text":"where the strategy has been applied in Kenya"},{"time":720869,"text":"for the recent elections,"},{"time":723515,"text":"and where there have been 500 interruptions in Iraq."}]},{"cues":[{"time":726688,"text":"So violence is responding as a disease"},{"time":729963,"text":"even as it behaves as a disease."},{"time":732228,"text":"So the theory, in a way,"},{"time":734431,"text":"is kind of being validated by the treatment."},{"time":738596,"text":"And recently, the Institute of Medicine"},{"time":741530,"text":"came out with a workshop report"},{"time":743667,"text":"which went through some of the data,"},{"time":745531,"text":"including the neuroscience,"},{"time":747076,"text":"on how this problem is really transmitted."}]},{"cues":[{"time":751399,"text":"So I think this is good news,"},{"time":754310,"text":"because it allows us an opportunity"},{"time":756174,"text":"to come out of the Middle Ages,"},{"time":757729,"text":"which is where I feel this field has been."},{"time":760771,"text":"It gives us an opportunity to consider the possibility"},{"time":763877,"text":"of replacing some of these prisons"},{"time":766673,"text":"with playgrounds or parks,"},{"time":769955,"text":"and to consider the possibility"},{"time":772623,"text":"of converting our neighborhoods into neighborhoods,"},{"time":776310,"text":"and to allow there to be a new strategy,"},{"time":779764,"text":"a new set of methods, a new set of workers:"},{"time":783625,"text":"science, in a way, replacing morality."},{"time":787040,"text":"And moving away from emotions"},{"time":789424,"text":"is the most important part of the solution"},{"time":792611,"text":"to science as a more important part of the solution."}]},{"cues":[{"time":796929,"text":"So I didn't mean to come up with this at all."},{"time":801652,"text":"It was a matter of,"},{"time":804154,"text":"I wanted actually a break,"},{"time":805985,"text":"and we looked at maps, we looked at graphs,"},{"time":810096,"text":"we asked some questions"},{"time":811733,"text":"and tried some tools"},{"time":814929,"text":"that actually have been used many times before"},{"time":817486,"text":"for other things."},{"time":819404,"text":"For myself, I tried to get away from"},{"time":822659,"text":"infectious diseases,"},{"time":824402,"text":"and I didn't."}]},{"cues":[{"time":826357,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":827984,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}